'''Beyond Bree J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar 1994''' was published by the [[American Mensa Tolkien Special Interest Group]] and edited by Sara Duniphine. The calendar features pen and ink illustrations by seven different artists inspired by [[The Hobbit]].

{{Beyond Bree (calendar)nav| J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar 1992| Calendar 2010}}

* Dimensions: 11 x 8.5 inches
* Stapled
* Manila envelope.
